snippet.title: Pirate Canvas
snippet.description: Hi I am Pirate Canvas, I am a youtuber, artist,, animator, and musician. On this channel I provide in-depth reviews on retro and modern video games, movies, and anime. I also do music, speedart, and other types of content that I believe people would be into. The best way to phrase it, this is a channel about me and what I am interested. If you are interested in the same stuff that I am then please subscribe as I try to upload content frequently.
